Source: cimplog
Version: 1.0.3
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/xmidt-org/cimplog.git
Upstream-Ref: v1.0.3
Build-Depends: cmake

Package: libcimplog
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple logging library - runtime
 cimplog is a simple logging library designed to work with RDK Logger.
 It provides a lightweight abstraction for logging functionality with
 support for different logging backends including generic logging,
 RDK logger integration, and onboarding logging features.
 .
 This package contains the runtime library.

Package: libcimplog-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: libcimplog (= ${version})
Description: Simple logging library - development files
 cimplog is a simple logging library designed to work with RDK Logger.
 It provides a lightweight abstraction for logging functionality with
 support for different logging backends.
 .
 This package contains headers and development files.
